WEBVTT

1
00:09:09.910 --> 00:09:12.750 
我很快就回来   我觉得他想和我谈谈
I'll be right back. I think he wants to talk.

2
00:09:12.950 --> 00:09:15.580 
你真是个好哥哥
You know, you are such a good brother.

3
00:09:15.790 --> 00:09:17.670 
谁说不是呢
You have no idea.

4
00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:24.760 
奶子
"Bosom"?

5
00:09:25.260 --> 00:09:27.180 
别提那了  你究竟在干什么?
Forget that. What the hell are you doing?

6
00:09:27.340 --> 00:09:30.930 
怎么了?  我正试图帮你说好话呢 虽然看来很不容易
What? I'm trying to make you look good. Turns out it's not that easy.

7
00:09:31.510 --> 00:09:33.930 
不  看起来你好象在说我很出色
You look like you're trying to make me look good...

8
00:09:34.100 --> 00:09:35.810 
但其实是在说你自己如何出色
...but you're making you look good.

9
00:09:35.980 --> 00:09:38.560 
我不知道你怎么做的但结果就是这样
I don't know how, but that's the net result.

10
00:09:38.730 --> 00:09:41.190 
- 艾伦这太荒唐了 - 是吗?  我不这么认为
- Alan, you're being ridiculous. - Am I? I think not.

